75.c
Student: – He like hotdog.
Teacher: – Third person singular, remember? Add -s.
Student: – Yes, sir. He likes hotdog.
Which type of corrective feedback is exemplified above?
      Repetition 
      Recast 
      Metalinguistic explanation 
      Elicitation 
      Clarification request


